  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.13.0\n\n### What happened?\n\nhttps://github.com/PaulRBerg/hardhat-template/issues/166\r\n\r\nIf I run the tests on the hardhat local network, it works fine.\r\nBut if I try it on Goerli or Sepolia network, it fails due to \"@nomicfoundation/hardhat-network-helpers\" package.\r\nCan you please provide me with a solution?\r\n![image](https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/assets/49041460/a9434bc2-b28c-4382-ba76-c8c10294e59c)\r\n\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\n- add some tests with `loadFixture` function from `@nomicfoundation/hardhat-network-helpers` package\r\n- run tests\r\n- it fails with `OnlyHardhatNetworkError: This helper can only be used with Hardhat Network. You are connected to 'sepolia'.`\n\n### Search terms\n\nhardhat test",
